title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show SEP-10-2013 TUES
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show SEP-10-2013 TUES









The Glenn Beck Radio Program - 9/10/13 




The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET




Glenn and the guys discuss Syria,
 and what our allies think of this and the impending situation.

 Has Russia has emerged as the world's true super power?

 And is America still even one?

 Glenn discusses how America may have lost its super power status last week.

 Also a breakdown on how the situation in Benghazi led us to the situation with Syria.

 And is Syria just a distraction from NSA details?

 Glenn talks about this, plus Vince Gill taking on the Westboro Bapist Church.

 And why is Tim Robbins not upset with Obama,  
 when he is doing the same things he accused George W. Bush of back in his administration?
